Class State

java.lang.Object
  State

public class State
extends java.lang.Object

This class is meant to hold one State of the eight puzzle game. A State holds a Node called path, which is a collection of the states visited in order to get to this state. The State function has a Manhantan Distance to calculate the heuristic value.

Author:
Keyean
